            "text_color": "#1c1c1c"
          }
        },
        "richtext_wrmDBa": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Maniére Noire was made for the moments that mark us and for celebrating the journey, the gathering of those who helped us rise, and the memories that deserve more than a fleeting cheer. It’s Champagne seen through the A Ma Maniére lens: bold in flavor, rich in feeling, and created for shared experiences.<br/></p>",
            "text_color": "#1c1c1c"
          }
        },
        "richtext_kWy6Hq": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A testament to A Ma Maniére’s enduring vision — where luxury meets legacy, and every creation carries intention — Maniére Noire embodies the essence of being <em>Built For This</em>: to rise, to create, and to celebrate with purpose.<br/><br/>The Maniére Noire Champagne will be available exclusively online at <a href=\"https://a-ma-maniere.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">a-ma-maniere.com.</span></a></p>",
            "text_color": "#1c1c1c"
          }
        }
      },
