    "beach_location_banner_L3FJnP": {
      "type": "beach-location-banner",
      "blocks": {
        "location_QyByL9": {
          "type": "location",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Appearance",
            "description": "<p>In the glass, it presents a captivating, brilliant salmon pink hue with shimmering copper reflections. A lively and persistent stream of fine bubbles creates a delicate, creamy mousse at the surface, indicating its quality and careful vinification.</p>"
          }
        },
        "location_P6PKMX": {
          "type": "location",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Aroma",
            "description": "<p>The nose is expressive and generous, bursting with an aromatic bouquet of ripe red fruits. Prominent notes of wild strawberry, raspberry, and redcurrant dominate, layered with subtle hints of cherry.</p>"
          }
        },
        "location_knPVtE": {
          "type": "location",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Palate",
            "description": "<p>The first sip reveals a pleasingly soft and round texture on the palate. The sweetness is well-integrated and beautifully counterbalanced by a crisp, clean acidity. The vibrant fruit flavors from the nose translate directly to the taste, with lush strawberry compote and sweet cherry taking center stage.</p>"
          }
        },
        "location_eTyzBP": {
          "type": "location",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Finish",
            "description": "<p>The finish is satisfyingly long and clean, leaving a lingering impression of sweet red berries and cream. The sweetness gently fades, allowing the acidity to lift the final notes and close with elegance and balance.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
